e rise to below 2 degrees Celsius and mitigate further impacts of climate change.'}, 'Additional context': "The document titled 'MetLink - Royal Meteorological Society IPCC 2021 - Evidence for Past Climate Change' serves as a resource discussing historical climate change data and the evidence pertaining to human impact."}